---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me | Personal Blog">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Who I Am</h2>
        <p>
          I exist in the spaces between definitions. Neither this nor that, but something more fluid and complex. 
          I am transgender, transient, transgressive—challenging the boundaries society tries to place around us.
        </p>
        <p>
          My words may comfort or confront. They might validate your experience or challenge your perspective. 
          Either way, they come from a place of radical honesty and the belief that art should disrupt as much as it delights.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What I Write About</h2>
        <p>
          My writing explores:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Identity</strong> — The masks we wear, the labels we adopt or reject, the fluidity of self</li>
          <li><strong>Boundaries</strong> — Those imposed on us and those we choose to cross or maintain</li>
          <li><strong>The Body</strong> — As political landscape, as canvas, as battlefield, as home</li>
          <li><strong>Modern Existence</strong> — Finding meaning in a fractured, digital world</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          I believe in creating spaces where vulnerability is strength and where questioning everything is the only way forward.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Connect</h2>
        <p>
          I'm not interested in performative community—I want real connection. Reach out if something resonates, if you disagree, if you want to collaborate on dismantling something that needs to fall.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a href="/blog" class="cta-button">Read My Writing</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-content {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about-section ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    list-style-type: none;
  }

  .about-section li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-section li::before {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }
</style>